title: Veebo - Virtual Party

creator: Veebo
descriptionHtml:
Making it easy to celebrate Life.


Party planning done right

Planning for a party can be like solving the hardest puzzle on the planet. So many steps must be taken in preparation to have a great party. Most people jump through rings of fire just to set up a simple get together. Luckily, when it comes to being a party planner, Veebo creates events across any avenue from a virtual visit to a house party!

We know how busy life is - work, family, friends, and even time for ourselves (if we can find it). Having to plan for multiple events while juggling all of our other responsibilities is a nightmare. With Veebo, you will be able to handle all of your planning needs. You can easily find family & friends then invite them and let the birthday countdown begin! We know some people cannot always make it to every function, but you can set up a virtual location so everyone can join regardless of where they are.

Personal party hub

Now that you have a virtual friend in us things can be done simply. During the preparation phase, you can set up group chats within Veebo so all hands are on deck always. You can also contact vendors if you need certain things ranging from bakers to florists. When it comes to party finder apps it’s uncommon to see a chat feature. We understand how vital this can be for any planner.

With other platforms like Zoom, users are cutoff during a video call unless they are paid subscribers. Veebo allows unlimited time for free. There shouldn’t be a limit placed on the time you spend with those you care about most! This is the virtual space to host any party or social event. With just a simple click, create unique invitations to add that special frosting on the cake!

Your event buddy

For the person who has all the things to do and places to be but can’t seem to find the time. No more being known as the person who always misses events - even your own birthday! With virtual reality, you will be able to attend or host as many events as you want with ease. We know that loved ones can be all over the world. Now, you can create a family link by setting up virtual parties just for them. We strive to make it easy for all to celebrate life with the people they care about.


FEATURES
- Create events
- Track events
- Share events
- Video camera accessibilities
- Group chat capabilities
- Calendar view
- Create birthday cards free
- Video chat and video calls

WRAP UP

Veebo is your virtual friend that is always by your side for any and all events. It's easy to send creative invitations, and with no time limits on video calls, the party never has to end!

DOWNLOAD Veebo today and get this party started!
